manufactured in the UK
@clearpay Partner

PARITET Group company is 29 years experienced manufacturer of uPVC and Aluminum windows and doors, largest Glass processor company in the South of Ukraine. We are expanding our exports to the USA, Canada and Europe, providing high-quality at affordable prices.

We use materials from the leading European suppliers, profile: Schuco, Reynaers, Aluprof, Kömmerling; glass: Saint-Gobain, Guardian.

Manufacturing lead time:
•	From 2 to 4 weeks for uPVC windows and doors;
•	From 1 to 3 weeks for glass showers, partitions, interior doors, fences and canopies;
•	From 6 to 8 weeks for Aluminum systems;
Delivery lead time:
•	From 5 to 7 days in Europe;
•	From month to 55 days to the ports of US;
•	From 45 to 65 days to the ports of Canada;

In one work shift we are capable to produce and recycle up to:
- 2000 glass units;
- 1500 sq.m. of tempered glass. 4 tons of tempered glass 
- having passed Heat Soak Test;
- 1000 sq.m. uPVC structures of various configurations and complexity;
- 25 tons of processed glass (glass edge and surface processing, modeling, lamination, decorating, strengthening);
- 350 sq.m. of constructions for facade glazing
- 100 sq.m. of aluminum window and door constructions of various configurations and complexity;

