KeonJinn is the expert of producing all kinds of LED mirrors for the project of hospitality,spa and salon, commercial, healthcare, senior living, multi-family and residential, retail industries  through the collaboration with interior designer, developer, architect, professional contractor, hospitality firm, chain stores and e-commerce sellers.  
We manufacture LED lighted bathroom mirrors with Fog-Free, Dimmable, Memory, Wall Switch/hardwired, Vertically/Horizontally functions, Upgrade Smart Mirrors plus bluetooth, temperature, date, clock function, Lighted Full-length Mirrors, Hollywood Makeup Mirrors, and Framed Mirrors with/without LED lighted.  
All our bathroom mirrors comply with USA/CA/Europe regulations and are safe for use in the bathroom Support environmental protection and sustainable development, cherish limited resource and source of energy and reduce customers’energy cost; 
Through all kinds of proposals,pursuit to beyond customer's expectation; 
Through untiring research and development,support high quality product and service;  
Our Value: Customer care is our top priority, there is a dedicated customer service team to help you during the whole throughout; 
Our Vision: Be The Best Expert Of ILLUMINATED Mirror ; 
Company Idea: Create the rich comfortable culture life base on the smart anti-fog mirror; 
We hope that customer can have the best shopping experience through our brand tonality: 
1.Less is more 2. Love 3. Happy Warm and Harmony.  
